# MultiEndpointPulse - HTTP Health Checker

MultiEndpointPulse is a lightweight tool for monitoring several APIs in real time.

## Features
- Logs status and response time  
- Retry handling  
- Configurable delay  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/30_MultiEndpointPulse.git
cd 30_MultiEndpointPulse
python monitor.py
